hopobject.body: How much were you paid in your last job? port credit village pharmacy - mississauga on Does it matter that Zimmerman followed Trayvon for no reason, that the dispatcher told him to stop, that he got out of his vehicle and confronted the kid with a loaded weapon? The fact that Trayvon was a better fighter than him does not mean Trayvon started the fight. By all accounts, Zimmerman started the fight. Seems to me that Zimmerman shooting the kid was Zimmerman’s fault, no matter whether Trayvon was on top or not.
